notes.name: Travelling Fantastical Circus
notes.legend: Roll up, roll up, this fantastical circus is here for a limited time only

notes.name: Eszi Melee
notes.legend: Warriors from around the land gather for a melee of the greats in Eszi, with fame, fortune and favour on offer to the victor

notes.name: Hawks migration
notes.legend: A huge group of hawks is migrating, though whether part of their annual routine, or something more extraordinary

notes.name: Crerags festival
notes.legend: A festival has been organised at Crerags as a chance to gather the nobility of the area together to be merry, make alliances and scheme around the crisis

notes.name: Entrancing mirage
notes.legend: This entrancing mirage has been luring travellers out of their way for eons

notes.legend: An element of the magic portal system connecting major cities. The portals were installed centuries ago, but still work fine
